    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted as complete. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated; seven factors show achieved levels below required levels, reflecting the high demands of MRL 5. Monte Carlo UQ results (TR-2027-UQ-VAD) confirm that 95th-percentile NIH predictions remain below the clinical hemolysis threshold across all operating points. The assessment package is approved for regulatory submission.",
